mkdir my_directory
Changing Directory:

bash
Copy code
cd my_directory
Creating a File:

bash
Copy code
touch my_file.txt
Editing a File (Using Nano Text Editor):

bash
Copy code
nano my_file.txt
Inside Nano, you can edit the file content. Press Ctrl + X to exit, Y to confirm changes, and then press Enter to save.

Displaying File Content:

bash
Copy code
cat my_file.txt
Removing a File:

bash
Copy code
rm my_file.txt
